    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/98ae5280bf07e0442390953b3b8ee20a.poster.avif?t=1732095825\" width=446 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/98ae5280bf07e0442390953b3b8ee20a.webm?t=1732095825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/98ae5280bf07e0442390953b3b8ee20a.mp4?t=1732095825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You always wanted to be the chef of your own teppanyaki style (aka hibachi style) restaurant,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >don't let your clumsiness get in the way of your dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Entertain your customers with your spectacular cooking skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >despite the awkward controls and wacky physics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>PLANNED UPDATES</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CUSTOMER REACTIONS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MORE CUSTOMER MODELS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UPGRADES</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/475eac6c93a06f6cb81a223dc38f99a4.avif?t=1732095825\" width=560 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AND OTHER WEIRD DREAMS BONUS STAGES</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/5705e08bdf8860cba8f011e4a7eb81ca.avif?t=1732095825\" width=560 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/9ad7484abf54b877f5f7b3535b30b78b.webp?t=1732095825\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/9ad7484abf54b877f5f7b3535b30b78b.poster.avif?t=1732095825\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/bea08ddc2b8e406ed0c5aa1ec6e3f51e.poster.avif?t=1732095825\" width=408 height=86 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/bea08ddc2b8e406ed0c5aa1ec6e3f51e.webm?t=1732095825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/bea08ddc2b8e406ed0c5aa1ec6e3f51e.mp4?t=1732095825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/9ad7484abf54b877f5f7b3535b30b78b.webp?t=1732095825\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304950/extras/9ad7484abf54b877f5f7b3535b30b78b.poster.avif?t=1732095825\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and more</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>HOW TO PLAY</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the mouse to move the spatula. Left Mouse Button to rotate the spatula.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold Right Mouse Button To move the spatula up and down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the &quot;ramp&quot;(transparent surface with arrows) to toss food on the plates. The food type should match the customers order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use mouse wheel to switch tools. Use the grabber to pick bottles hold Middle Mouse Button to open and release to close and grab the bottle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
